name: Peanut Gas Tank
description: Custom peanut style gas tank. Holds about 3/4 of a gallon of gas, and it comes with frame mount hardware, gas cap, and petcock. They come grey powder coat.

name: Shwimperial Shirt
description: Vintage Schwinn inspired logo - imperial cycles design. Gold print on front and gold Imperial Cycles crown logo on the back. Shirts come in heather grey color, black, charcoal grey, and white. Also, Shirts come in sizes small, medium, large, x-large, 2x-large

name: Pedal And Destroy Shirt
description: Inspired by the thrasher skate and destroy shirt design. Shirt comes in black, heather grey, white, and come in sizes Large, X-Large, Double X-large.

name: Greatest T-shirt
description: Greatest Shirt - Top 5 contending vintage beach cruiser companies. Monark, Schwinn, Columbia, Roadmaster, & Shelby with Helvetica font with top 5 list design. Shirt comes only in black with white ink, with imperial cycles crown logo on the back. Shirts also come in sizes small, medium, large, x-large, and 2x-large.
